title: BEST LINE IN SLS LUX!!!
posting_body: ['The Absolute best line in SLS Lux with spectacular skyline views.', 'Take a private elevator w/biometrics technology.', 'This Unfurnished 3 Bedroom + Den with 4 full Bathrooms is the perfect residence to live in!', 'Enjoy Smart home technology, porcelain title floors throughout, Italian cabinets, rain showers and a spacious wrap around balcony.', 'The amenities include SLS LUX Spa & room service from the Katsura restaurant/bar, access to the rooftop & pool, 2 story cava lounge, Jacuzzi, Tennis court, rock-climbing wall, basketball court & full service fitness center and so much more!', 'Few steps from Brickell City Center and the best restaurants in town.', "Won't last!", 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
